metadata.name: Elegance
metadata.description:
This wonderful photo is the result of one of many relaxing afternoons sipping coffee and dancing around with my dear friend Elizabeth. She's an amazing dancer, teacher, mother, painter, and friend and I'm thankful for the years of building pictures together.

Mamiya RZ67 + Mamiya 110 f/2.8 + Kodak Portra 160 (hand developed in my kitchen sink and scanned with care ^_^)
